{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_15111.jpg","bgm":"bgm23_tokime03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":770200}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Ah, there you are!@I have something I want to ask you about!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Wait, what?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":770200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Earlier, I wrote down what the store clerk@at the 1090 told me..."},{"chara":[{"id":770200}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I don't really understand what they meant,@so I would like you to explain it to me."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...W-what were they saying?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":770200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Uh...well, allow me to demonstrate."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Demonstrate...?"},{"chara":[{"id":770200,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...We're often visited by influencers."},{"chara":[{"id":770200}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"It creates an incredible synergy,@in a way, it's kind of sustainable?"},{"chara":[{"id":770200,"motion":200},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102501}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"We have evidence, and we've@reached a consensus too~"},{"chara":[{"id":770200,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"It's just like diversity, right?@It really boosts my motivation too~"},{"chara":[{"id":770200,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...Is what they said."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":770200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I have no idea what they're talking about..."},{"chara":[{"id":770200,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"So please, teach me!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"We can't..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"What do you think...?"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...Yeah, well...I see..."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...No, I can't figure it out either!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"I knew it..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"After all, I'm still studying!"},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"From now on, we're all going to learn together!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Hmm, I see... I'd like to know what they meant..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102501,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...Aha!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Here she is...our teacher!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"Huh?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Wh-Where are you going?!"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...Everyone, allow me to introduce you to our@expert on the modern Land of the Rising Sun..."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"This is Kagome Satori-sensei!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"EEEH?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Please! Grant us your knowledge!"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"You definitely know a lot more than we do!"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"No, that's not true..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Well then, Teacher, let's get started!@What is an \"influencer\"...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...Ah, does that mean...someone that's influential...?"},{"chara":[{"id":770200}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Oh! I see!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Just as I predicted!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"W-wait a second! I came here for an interview...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":770200,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"What is \"synergy\"?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...\"Teamwork\"..."},{"chara":[{"id":770200,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Amazing!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Chiharu","textLeft":"Let's keep going!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Sunao","textLeft":"She's open to any further questions you have!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Wait! Please, wait a minute!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11_another/208101_aruchang.png","posX":0,"posY":-70,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm20_song10","nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Kagome was bombarded with questions@after that, and it was tough...>","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<She answered question after question herself, so@in the end, she was the one who got interviewed...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Kagome, you seemed to be enjoying yourself@somehow...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<...But, I see...that's right...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<At this time...@No, even before this...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Kagome had made up her mind...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<That makes things a little complicated for me...>"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
